    <h1 class="opener__hed  opener__hed--vertical-rule -is-over-bg opener__hed--light opener__hed--small" >        Clarence Thomas Secretly Participated in Koch Network Donor Events
    </h1>

    
            <div class="article-meta-1  -is-over-bg article-meta-1--light">
            <span class="article-meta-1__byline">
                by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/joshua-kaplan">Joshua Kaplan</a>, <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/justin-elliott">Justin Elliott</a> and <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/alex-mierjeski">Alex Mierjeski</a>            </span>
            <time class="article-meta-1__pubdate">
                <time class="timestamp" datetime="2023-09-22EDT05:00">Sept. 22, 5 a.m. EDT</time>
            </time>
        </div>
    
    </div> <!-- Close .opener__topic-title-dek-wrapper -->

        <div class="content"> <!-- not sure if this is the best way to reestablish the text column -->
        <h2 class="opener__dek opener__dek--match-text-column" >            Thomas has attended at least two Koch donor summits, putting him in the extraordinary position of having helped a political network that has brought multiple cases before the Supreme Court.
        </h2>
    </div>
    
</div>
        
<div class="article-meta-1
